Package: devops-toolkit
Architecture: all
Depends: bash (>= 4.0), curl, git, docker.io | docker-ce, python3, php-cli, gum, arp-scan
Description: DevOps Toolkit - Collection of development and deployment scripts
 A comprehensive collection of development scripts including:
 - Django project creator with multiple templates
 - PHP version switcher
 - Advanced network troubleshooting and scanning tools
 - SSH connection manager with device discovery
 - Storage management utilities with symlink support
 - Download manager
 - Laravel starter scripts
 .
 This toolkit helps developers and DevOps engineers automate common tasks
 and streamline their development workflow. Features interactive menus,
 network device discovery, MAC address detection, and advanced SSH management.
